  </div>
</section>

{# ── INDUSTRY ROUTING · 6 CA state-weighted verticals → .rel-card grid (r-3), each links its child ── #}
<section class="sec reveal" id="ca-industries-hub-grid">
  <div class="ct">
    <div class="idx"><span class="idx__n">§</span><span class="idx__t">California-weighted verticals</span><span class="idx__rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:10px;">Six California industries we build books for.</h2>
